# ============================================================
# Apartamentos — Maestro de alojamientos
# ============================================================

### 1. Listar apartamentos activos
GET {{base}}/api/apartamentos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Crear apartamento manual
POST {{base}}/api/apartamentos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Apartamento Sol 101",
  "ciudad": "Sevilla",
  "direccion": "Calle Sol, 101, 1ºA",
  "id_externo": "APT101"
}

###

### 3. Crear apartamento sin nombre → 422
POST {{base}}/api/apartamentos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ciudad": "Sevilla"
}

###

### 4. Detalle de apartamento
# Sustituir <uuid> por el id devuelto en la creación
GET {{base}}/api/apartamentos/<uuid>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Detalle de apartamento inexistente → 404
GET {{base}}/api/apartamentos/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Actualizar apartamento
PUT {{base}}/api/apartamentos/<uuid>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Apartamento Sol 101 — Renovado",
  "ciudad": "Sevilla",
  "direccion": "Calle Sol, 101, 2ºB"
}

###

### 7. Soft-delete de apartamento
DELETE {{base}}/api/apartamentos/<uuid>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Sincronizar desde Smoobu (requiere PMS configurado)
POST {{base}}/api/apartamentos/sincronizacion/smoobu
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Sincronizar sin PMS configurado → 400
# (empresa sin configuracion_pms)
POST {{base}}/api/apartamentos/sincronizacion/smoobu
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sin_pms}}

###

### 10. Leer configuración PMS
GET {{base}}/api/apartamentos/pms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Guardar configuración PMS
PUT {{base}}/api/apartamentos/pms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proveedor": "smoobu",
  "api_key": "sk-smoobu-test-key-123"
}

###

### 12. Eliminar configuración PMS
DELETE {{base}}/api/apartamentos/pms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. Preview de importación XLSX (multipart)
# Requiere archivo .xlsx real con cabeceras reconocidas
POST {{base}}/api/apartamentos/importacion/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="apartamentos.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./apartamentos_ejemplo.xlsx
------Boundary--
